        <article>
            <p>In 2026, India's job market remains highly competitive — especially for freshers, young professionals, and people in tier-2/3 cities like Patna, Bihar. Traditional job portals force candidates into endless applications with little feedback or real visibility to recruiters.</p>
            
            <p>That’s exactly what <strong><a href="https://www.requirehire.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RequireHire.com</a></strong> changes. As India's pioneering <strong>interview-first recruitment platform</strong>, RequireHire flips the script: <em>skills speak first</em>, not resumes. With AI-powered tools, verified profiles, and direct access to companies, it dramatically increases your chances of getting noticed and hired — fast.</p>

            <h2>What Makes RequireHire Different from others ?</h2>
            <p>Most platforms list jobs → you apply → wait (often forever). RequireHire starts with <strong>you getting interviewed</strong> — either via AI pre-screening or directly by HR.</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Interview-First Philosophy</strong> — "Get Interviewed. Not Just Listed."</li>
                <li><strong>AI-Powered Voice Mock Interviews</strong> — Practice naturally, speak answers, receive instant feedback on communication, confidence & content.</li>
                <li><strong>Skill-Based Scoring</strong> — Objective AI ranks your real abilities, helping companies discover talent beyond resumes.</li>
                <li><strong>Verified Profiles Only</strong> — Builds trust; no fake applications waste time.</li>
                <li><strong>Direct HR Access</strong> — Companies reach out to shortlisted candidates — no ghosting.</li>
                <li><strong>100% Free for Candidates</strong> — All core features (mocks, scoring, applications) are completely free forever.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How RequireHire Actually Works (Step-by-Step)</h2>
            
            <h3>1. Create & Verify Your Profile</h3>
            <p>Sign up at <a href="https://www.requirehire.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener">requirehire.com</a>. Add your details — education, skills, experience. Verification ensures authenticity.</p>

            <h3>2. Practice with AI Voice Mock Interviews</h3>
            <p>Use the built-in AI interviewer (powered by advanced models). Speak naturally in English or Hindi. Get real-time scores and detailed feedback on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Clarity & confidence</li>
                <li>Technical accuracy</li>
                <li>Relevance to job roles (IT, Medical, Banking, Government, etc.)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>3. Get Your AI Skill Score</h3>
            <p>After mocks and profile completion, receive an objective skill score. This becomes your "match power" — companies see ranked, interview-ready candidates instantly.</p>

            <h3>4. Get Discovered & Interviewed Directly</h3>
            <p>Verified profiles appear in company searches. HR teams invite top matches for live interviews — skipping resume black holes.</p>

            <h3>5. Land the Job Faster</h3>
            <p>Many users report significantly reduced time-to-hire (up to 50% faster than traditional methods). Employers save time; candidates gain real opportunities.</p>

